title: HOLDING THE RAMPARTS - Elder Scrolls: Total War - Stormcloaks Campaign #4
description:
HOLDING THE RAMPARTS - Elder Scrolls: Total War - Stormcloaks Campaign #4 - The Empire has decided to launch their attack on Dawnstar and Fort Dunstad.  The brave Stormcloaks are at the ramparts and ready to hold.  The new aspiring Commander who lead the new grand army will have many new challenges ahead of them.  Enjoy the Video :D
